spec_data.Name: pycscope
spec_data.Description:
A python script to generate a cscope index from a Python source tree. pycscope
uses Python's own parser and AST to generate the index, so it is a bit more
accurate than plain cscope.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:09:30 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Generates a cscope index of Python source trees
